
---

## ⚙️ `setup/create_persistent_usb.sh`

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# Create persistence for Linux Mint using Ventoy
# Usage: sudo bash create_persistent_usb.sh /dev/sdX linuxmint.iso

DEVICE="$1"
ISO="$2"

if [ -z "$DEVICE" ] || [ -z "$ISO" ]; then
    echo "Usage: sudo bash $0 /dev/sdX linuxmint.iso"
    exit 1
fi

echo "[*] Creating persistence partition on $DEVICE..."
sudo ventoy -P -s /path/to/persistence.dat -d "$DEVICE"

echo "[*] Persistence setup complete."
